{"tid":1124844,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟我係咪濕氣重","createTime":"2019-04-25T09:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T18:07:56.000Z","uid":202926,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f222e6a8be2f965bca8f560b968c4ece88f8f238","tid":1124844,"uid":202926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月訓極都唔夠 <br />\n長期都冇精冇神咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭又好似有野lun住咁 由期係額頭兩側 好唔清爽<br />\n喉嚨又kepp住有痰 又柯爛屎<br />\n睇過中醫 食過中藥都冇乜效<br />\n以為過左潮濕天氣會好啲 但都係咁<br />\n究竟我係咪濕重<br />\n有冇中醫巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10baa4aa2cb3b23ad184cfbe2876035ff8fd6aeb","tid":1124844,"uid":56199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"係，睇過第二個中醫啦"},{"pid":"060b520cb9cfe583ae8f771c37977581f0b9bbf0","tid":1124844,"uid":55321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:36:05.000Z","msg":"證明你個中醫垃圾"},{"pid":"045a97b0131ddbc68c556dff9a0cc3283020cf79","tid":1124844,"uid":136776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"多做運動 好過睇醫生"},{"pid":"7f7a1edb3fb8f8201627bbe12b9d6f24cc127cd5","tid":1124844,"uid":41352,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"搵師父睇下好啲，可能有野跟住你"},{"pid":"aced85fa3ad3fade3a6c508845db983afe6f7290","tid":1124844,"uid":148252,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"拔罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6d75c5d70bd5bdf576e54cf7d77c030483cba3","tid":1124844,"uid":202926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f7a1edb3fb8f8201627bbe12b9d6f24cc127cd5","tid":1124844,"uid":41352,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:39:55.000Z",